&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241018" rel="nofollow"&gt;Fri, 18 Oct 2024 16:24:34 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
