&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; interoperability with Edge
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; In order to finally ship this feature, should we aim for compliance
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; with the spec or interoperability with Edge's current behavior?
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On Monday, November 21, 2016 at 8:03:51 PM UTC+1, Harald Alvestrand
