&gt;
&gt; Summary
&gt;
&gt; The PushMessageData interface mimics the Body interface, which was amended
&gt; earlier this year with a new bytes() method, following the principle that
&gt; APIs should generally vend byte buffers as Uint8Arrays.
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/push-api/pull/370"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/push-api/pull/370&lt;/a&gt;
