&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Support of `sideways-rl` and `sideways-lr` keywords for `writing-mode`
&gt;&gt;&gt; CSS property is added. They are vertical writing modes, and all letters are
&gt;&gt;&gt; sideways.
