&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://groups.google.com/u/1/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/gGHOmFGEzQ0"&gt;https://groups.google.com/u/1/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/gGHOmFGEzQ0&lt;/a&gt;
